text: Cindy van der Zanden (born 10 July 1993) is a Dutch softball player. She is member of the Netherlands women's national softball team. With the national team she became European champion at the 2022 Women's Softball European Championship. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch softball players Category:Sportspeople from Rotterdam Category:Sportswomen
